{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":927,"text":"I want to talk to you about one thing"},{"time":3108,"text":"and just one thing only,"},{"time":4864,"text":"and this has to do with when people ask me,"},{"time":8620,"text":"what do you do?"},{"time":11867,"text":"To which I usually respond,"},{"time":13767,"text":"I do computer music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16907,"text":"Now, a number of people"},{"time":18852,"text":"just stop talking to me right then and there,"},{"time":21089,"text":"and the rest who are left usually have"},{"time":23502,"text":"this blank look in their eye,"},{"time":25750,"text":"as if to say, what does that mean?"},{"time":27919,"text":"And I feel like I'm actually depriving them"},{"time":30137,"text":"of information by telling them this,"},{"time":33342,"text":"at which point I usually panic"},{"time":35070,"text":"and spit out the first thing that comes to my mind,"},{"time":36660,"text":"which is, I have no idea what I'm doing."},{"time":40442,"text":"Which is true."},{"time":42054,"text":"That's usually followed by a second thought,"},{"time":44910,"text":"which is, whatever it is that I'm doing,"},{"time":48210,"text":"I love it."},{"time":49902,"text":"And today, I want to, well,"},{"time":53699,"text":"share with you something I love,"},{"time":55870,"text":"and also why."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57354,"text":"And I think we'll begin with just this question:"},{"time":61283,"text":"What is computer music?"},{"time":62620,"text":"And I'm going to try to do my\nbest to provide a definition,"},{"time":66400,"text":"maybe by telling you a story"},{"time":68131,"text":"that goes through some of the stuff"},{"time":69778,"text":"I've been working on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71704,"text":"And the first thing, I think, in our story"},{"time":73516,"text":"is going to be something called ChucK."},{"time":76064,"text":"Now, ChucK is a programming language for music,"},{"time":81437,"text":"and it's open-source, it's freely available,"},{"time":84146,"text":"and I like to think that it crashes equally well"},{"time":86066,"text":"on all modern operating systems."},{"time":88410,"text":"And instead of telling you more about it,"},{"time":91370,"text":"I'm just going to give you a demo."},{"time":93196,"text":"By the way, I'm just going to nerd out"},{"time":94352,"text":"for just a few minutes here,"},{"time":95981,"text":"so I would say, don't freak out."},{"time":98779,"text":"In fact, I would invite all of you to join me"},{"time":100850,"text":"in just geeking out."},{"time":102034,"text":"If you've never written a line\nof code before in your life,"},{"time":105096,"text":"do not worry."},{"time":106282,"text":"I'll bet you'll be able to come along on this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109799,"text":"First thing I'm going to do is to make"},{"time":111218,"text":"a sine wave oscillator,"},{"time":113051,"text":"and we're going to called the sine wave generator"},{"time":116085,"text":"\"Ge.\""},{"time":118847,"text":"And then we're going to connect \"Ge\" to the DAC."},{"time":120937,"text":"Now this is kind of the abstraction"},{"time":122091,"text":"for the sound output on my computer. Okay?"},{"time":124699,"text":"So I've connected myself into the speaker."},{"time":127899,"text":"Next, I'm going to say my frequency"},{"time":129491,"text":"is 440 hertz,"},{"time":131459,"text":"and I'm going to let time advance"},{"time":135278,"text":"by two seconds through this operation."},{"time":138000,"text":"All right, so if I were to play this --"},{"time":142068,"text":"(Tone) —"},{"time":144740,"text":"you would hear a sine wave\nat 440 hertz for two seconds."},{"time":147161,"text":"Okay, great. Now I'm going to copy and paste this,"},{"time":150187,"text":"and then just change some of these numbers,"},{"time":151931,"text":"220.5, 440 I shall leave it as that,"},{"time":155891,"text":"and .5 and 880."},{"time":158331,"text":"By doubling the frequency,"},{"time":159693,"text":"we're actually going up in successive octaves,"},{"time":162210,"text":"and then we have this sequence --"},{"time":163547,"text":"(Tones) — of tones."},{"time":165674,"text":"Okay, great, now I can imagine creating"},{"time":167580,"text":"all kinds of really horrible"},{"time":169022,"text":"single sine wave pieces of music with this,"},{"time":171420,"text":"but I'm going to do something\nthat computers are really good at,"},{"time":174332,"text":"which is repetition."},{"time":176156,"text":"I'm going to put this all in a while loop,"},{"time":177860,"text":"and you actually don't need to indent,"},{"time":179156,"text":"but this is purely for aesthetic reasons."},{"time":181280,"text":"It's good practice."},{"time":182884,"text":"And when we do this —"},{"time":184464,"text":"(Tones) —"},{"time":188961,"text":"that's going to go on for a while."},{"time":190134,"text":"In fact, it's probably not going to stop"},{"time":191628,"text":"until this computer disintegrates."},{"time":193411,"text":"And I can't really empirically prove that to you,"},{"time":196110,"text":"but I hope you'll believe me when I say that."},{"time":199779,"text":"Next, I'm going to replace this 220"},{"time":201655,"text":"by math.random2f."},{"time":204461,"text":"I'm going to generate a random number"},{"time":205739,"text":"between 30 and 1,000 and send that"},{"time":208879,"text":"to the frequency of me."},{"time":210965,"text":"And I'm going to do this every half a second."},{"time":213065,"text":"(Tones)"},{"time":216007,"text":"Let's do this every 200 milliseconds."},{"time":218668,"text":"(Tones)"},{"time":223290,"text":"One hundred."},{"time":224745,"text":"(Tones)"},{"time":226357,"text":"All right."},{"time":227591,"text":"At this point, we've reached something"},{"time":229535,"text":"that I would like to think of as"},{"time":230605,"text":"the canonical computer music."},{"time":234626,"text":"This is, to me, the sound that mainframes"},{"time":238443,"text":"are supposed to be making"},{"time":239565,"text":"when they're thinking really hard."},{"time":242807,"text":"It's this sound, it's like,"},{"time":244900,"text":"the square root of five million."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250427,"text":"So is this computer music?"},{"time":254211,"text":"Yeah, I guess by definition,"},{"time":256190,"text":"it's kind of computer music."},{"time":257395,"text":"It's probably not the kind of music you would listen to"},{"time":260403,"text":"cruising down the highway,"},{"time":261891,"text":"but it's a foundation of computer-generated music,"},{"time":266907,"text":"and using ChucK,"},{"time":269110,"text":"we've actually been building instruments"},{"time":270803,"text":"in the Stanford Laptop Orchestra,"},{"time":272699,"text":"based right here at Stanford Center for\nComputer Research in Music and Acoustics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276900,"text":"Now the Laptop Orchestra is an ensemble of laptops,"},{"time":279683,"text":"humans and special hemispherical speaker arrays."},{"time":282312,"text":"Now the reason we have these"},{"time":283909,"text":"is so that for the instruments that we create"},{"time":286379,"text":"out of the laptop, we want the sound to come"},{"time":288603,"text":"out of somewhere near the instrument"},{"time":291123,"text":"and the performer,"},{"time":292491,"text":"kind of much like a traditional, acoustic instrument."},{"time":295193,"text":"Like, if I were to play a violin here,"},{"time":297079,"text":"the sound would naturally not come out of"},{"time":299190,"text":"the P.A. system, but from the artifact itself."},{"time":301964,"text":"So these speakers are meant to emulate that."},{"time":305171,"text":"In fact, I'm going to show you"},{"time":306500,"text":"how we actually built them."},{"time":309243,"text":"The first step is to go to IKEA"},{"time":311307,"text":"and buy a salad bowl."},{"time":312687,"text":"This is an 11-inch Blanda Matt."},{"time":315917,"text":"That's the actual name,"},{"time":317415,"text":"and I actually use one of these"},{"time":318837,"text":"to make salad at home as well, I kid you not."},{"time":321065,"text":"And the first step is you turn it upside down,"},{"time":324236,"text":"and then you drill holes in them,"},{"time":326711,"text":"six holes per hemi,"},{"time":329220,"text":"and then make a base plate,"},{"time":330934,"text":"put car speaker drivers in them"},{"time":333614,"text":"along with amplifiers in the enclosure,"},{"time":336205,"text":"and you put that all together and you have"},{"time":337559,"text":"these hemispherical speaker arrays."},{"time":339333,"text":"Add people, add laptops,"},{"time":340896,"text":"you have a laptop orchestra."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343584,"text":"And what might a laptop orchestra sound like?"},{"time":347114,"text":"Well, let me give you a demonstration"},{"time":349033,"text":"of about 200 instruments we've created so far"},{"time":352268,"text":"for the Laptop Orchestra."},{"time":355511,"text":"And what I'm going to do is\nactually come over to this thing."},{"time":357938,"text":"This thing I have in front of me"},{"time":360143,"text":"actually used to be a commodity gaming controller"},{"time":363355,"text":"called a Gametrak."},{"time":365145,"text":"This thing actually has a glove\nyou can put on your hands."},{"time":367021,"text":"It's tethered to the base,"},{"time":368581,"text":"and this will track the position of your hands"},{"time":371110,"text":"in real time."},{"time":372163,"text":"It was originally designed as a golfing controller"},{"time":375537,"text":"to detect the motion of your swing."},{"time":377453,"text":"That turned out to be a rather large"},{"time":379984,"text":"commercial non-success,"},{"time":381688,"text":"at which point they slashed prices to 10 dollars,"},{"time":385442,"text":"at which point computer music researchers"},{"time":387450,"text":"said, \"This is awesome!"},{"time":389508,"text":"We can prototype instruments out of this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":392257,"text":"So let me show you one instrument we've created,"},{"time":395201,"text":"one of many, and this instrument"},{"time":397113,"text":"is called \"Twilight,\""},{"time":398682,"text":"and it's meant to go with this metaphor"},{"time":401368,"text":"of pulling a sound out of the ground."},{"time":404401,"text":"So let me see if this will work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407752,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":416968,"text":"And put it back."},{"time":418791,"text":"And then if you go to the left,"},{"time":422886,"text":"right,"},{"time":429427,"text":"it sounds like an elephant in pain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433231,"text":"This is a slightly metallic sound."},{"time":436259,"text":"Turn it just a bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439613,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":445211,"text":"It's like a hovering car."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452406,"text":"Okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453799,"text":"This third one is a ratchet-like interaction, so"},{"time":459360,"text":"let me turn it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464915,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":470068,"text":"So it's a slightly different interaction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471948,"text":"The fourth one is a drone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475583,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":488613,"text":"And finally, let's see,"},{"time":491319,"text":"this is a totally different interaction,"},{"time":493130,"text":"and I think you have to imagine that there's"},{"time":494940,"text":"this giant invisible drum sitting right here on stage,"},{"time":497872,"text":"and I'm going to bang it."},{"time":502255,"text":"(Drum)"},{"time":504902,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":508241,"text":"So there we go, so that's one of many instruments"},{"time":510685,"text":"in the Laptop Orchestra."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512455,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516009,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518290,"text":"And when you put that together,"},{"time":520396,"text":"you get something that sounds like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524464,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573470,"text":"Okay, and so, I think from the experience"},{"time":575820,"text":"of building a lot of instruments\nfor the Laptop Orchestra,"},{"time":578343,"text":"and I think from the curiosity of wondering,"},{"time":580847,"text":"what if we took these"},{"time":582350,"text":"hopefully expressive instruments"},{"time":583942,"text":"and we brought it to a lot of people,"},{"time":586575,"text":"plus then a healthy bout of insanity —"},{"time":588982,"text":"put those three things together —"},{"time":590471,"text":"led to me actually co-founding a startup company"},{"time":593987,"text":"in 2008 called Smule."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596446,"text":"Now Smule's mission is to create"},{"time":598366,"text":"expressive, mobile music things,"},{"time":602223,"text":"and one of the first musical instruments"},{"time":606985,"text":"we created is called Ocarina."},{"time":608845,"text":"And I'm going to just demo this for you real quick."},{"time":615234,"text":"So Ocarina —"},{"time":617650,"text":"(Music) —"},{"time":621248,"text":"is based on this ancient flute-like instrument"},{"time":624371,"text":"called the ocarina,"},{"time":625780,"text":"and this one is the four-hole\nEnglish pendant configuration,"},{"time":629163,"text":"and you're literally blowing into the microphone"},{"time":632566,"text":"to make the sound."},{"time":635492,"text":"And there's actually a little ChucK script"},{"time":637125,"text":"running in here that's detecting"},{"time":638293,"text":"the strength of your blowing"},{"time":639775,"text":"and also synthesizing the sound."},{"time":641893,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":645478,"text":"And vibrato is mapped to the accelerometer,"},{"time":648808,"text":"so you can get —"},{"time":650461,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":653790,"text":"All right. So let me play a little ditty for you,"},{"time":659533,"text":"a little Bach."},{"time":661349,"text":"And here, you'll hear a little\naccompaniment with the melody."},{"time":663941,"text":"The accompaniment actually follows the melody,"},{"time":666509,"text":"not the other way around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670290,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":683132,"text":"And this was designed"},{"time":684789,"text":"to let you take your time"},{"time":686065,"text":"and figure out where your expressive space is,"},{"time":689270,"text":"and you can just hang out here"},{"time":691077,"text":"for a while, for a really\ndramatic effect, if you want,"},{"time":694139,"text":"and whenever you're ready —"}]},{"cues":[{"time":697205,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":712981,"text":"And on these longer notes,"},{"time":714089,"text":"I'm going to use more vibrato"},{"time":716190,"text":"towards the end of the notes"},{"time":717082,"text":"to give it a little bit more of an expressive quality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720134,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":727473,"text":"Huh, that's a nice chord to end this excerpt on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731160,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":734581,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":739750,"text":"So I think a good question to ask about Ocarina is,"},{"time":743746,"text":"is this a toy or it an instrument? Maybe it's both,"},{"time":748493,"text":"but for me, I think the more important question is,"},{"time":750502,"text":"is it expressive?"},{"time":752043,"text":"And at the same time, I think"},{"time":754117,"text":"creating these types of instruments"},{"time":755421,"text":"asks a question about the role of technology,"},{"time":758783,"text":"and its place for how we make music."},{"time":760477,"text":"Apparently, for example,"},{"time":762214,"text":"not that long ago, like only a hundred years ago —"},{"time":764120,"text":"that's not that long in the course of human history —"},{"time":765640,"text":"families back then"},{"time":767621,"text":"used to make music together"},{"time":769509,"text":"as a common form of entertainment."},{"time":772557,"text":"I don't think that's really happening"},{"time":773802,"text":"that much anymore."},{"time":775337,"text":"You know, this is before radio, before recording."},{"time":777007,"text":"In the last hundred years, with all this technology,"},{"time":779214,"text":"we now have more access to music"},{"time":781388,"text":"as listeners and consumers,"},{"time":783021,"text":"but somehow, I think we're making less music"},{"time":786084,"text":"than ever before."},{"time":787770,"text":"I'm not sure why that would be."},{"time":789401,"text":"Maybe it's because it's too easy just to hit play."},{"time":792050,"text":"And while listening to music is wonderful,"},{"time":794509,"text":"there's a special joy to making music"},{"time":797918,"text":"that's all its own."},{"time":799573,"text":"And I think that's one part"},{"time":800836,"text":"of the goal of why I do what I do"},{"time":802926,"text":"is kind of to take us back to the past a little bit. Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":807682,"text":"Now, if that's one goal, the other goal"},{"time":809462,"text":"is to look to the future and think about"},{"time":810892,"text":"what kind of new musical things can we make"},{"time":813229,"text":"that we don't perhaps yet have names for"},{"time":815822,"text":"that's enabled by technology, but ultimately"},{"time":818685,"text":"might change the way that humans make music."},{"time":821126,"text":"And I'll just give you one example here,"},{"time":823498,"text":"and this is Ocarina's other feature."},{"time":829723,"text":"This is a globe,"},{"time":831910,"text":"and here you're actually listening"},{"time":834683,"text":"to other users of Ocarina"},{"time":836735,"text":"blow into their iPhones to play something."},{"time":840715,"text":"This is \"G.I.R.\" from Texas,"},{"time":845568,"text":"\"R.I.K.\" I don't know why it's these\nthree-letter names today, Los Angeles."},{"time":851501,"text":"They're all playing pretty,"},{"time":856519,"text":"somewhat minimal music here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":859879,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":865327,"text":"And the idea with this is that, well,"},{"time":867933,"text":"technology should not be foregrounded here,"},{"time":871850,"text":"and — (Laughter) —"},{"time":873933,"text":"we've actually opened this up."},{"time":876646,"text":"The first thought is that, hey, you know"},{"time":878153,"text":"there's somebody somewhere out there"},{"time":881343,"text":"playing some music,"},{"time":882613,"text":"and this is a small but I think important"},{"time":884393,"text":"human connection to make"},{"time":885613,"text":"that perhaps the technology affords."}]},{"cues":[{"time":888611,"text":"As a final example,"},{"time":891435,"text":"and perhaps my favorite example,"},{"time":892790,"text":"is that in the wake of the 2011 earthquake"},{"time":895941,"text":"and tsunami disaster in Japan,"},{"time":898427,"text":"a woman reached out in one of our singing apps"},{"time":901270,"text":"to try to get people to join in to sing with her"},{"time":904157,"text":"on a version of \"Lean on Me.\""},{"time":905762,"text":"Now, in these apps, there's this thing that allows"},{"time":908810,"text":"any user to add their voice"},{"time":910511,"text":"to an existing performance by any other user"},{"time":913309,"text":"or group of users,"},{"time":914363,"text":"so in some sense, she's created this kind of"},{"time":916388,"text":"global ad hoc corral of strangers,"},{"time":919772,"text":"and within weeks, thousands of people"},{"time":921980,"text":"joined in on this,"},{"time":923612,"text":"and you can kind of see people\ncoming from all around the world"},{"time":925991,"text":"and all these lines converging on the origin"},{"time":928272,"text":"where the first rendition of the song was sung,"},{"time":930620,"text":"and that's in Tokyo."},{"time":932254,"text":"And this is what it sounds like \nwhen there's 1,000 people."},{"time":935686,"text":"This is 1,000 voices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":937663,"text":"(Recording) ♪ Sometimes in our lives ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":941940,"text":"♪ We all have pain, we all have sorrow ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":949260,"text":"♪ But if we are wise ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":953100,"text":"♪ We know that there's always tomorrow ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":958990,"text":"♪ Lean on me ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":961497,"text":"♪ When you're not strong ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":964310,"text":"♪ And I'll be your friend ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":966950,"text":"♪ I'll help you carry on ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":971235,"text":"♪ For it won't be long ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":975248,"text":"♪ Till I'm gonna need ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":977976,"text":"♪ Somebody to lean on ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":981372,"text":"♪ Just lean on — ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":983726,"text":"Is this computer music?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":985296,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":990728,"text":"Was that computer music?"},{"time":992696,"text":"Yeah, I guess so; it's something that you really"},{"time":994743,"text":"couldn't have done without computers."},{"time":997028,"text":"But at the same time, it's also just human,"},{"time":1001264,"text":"and I think what I've essentially answered so far"},{"time":1004353,"text":"is maybe why I do the stuff that I do,"},{"time":1007744,"text":"and let's just finally return to the first question:"},{"time":1010136,"text":"What is computer music?"},{"time":1012248,"text":"And I think that the catch here is that,"},{"time":1014552,"text":"at least to me, computer music"},{"time":1015808,"text":"isn't really about computers."},{"time":1017656,"text":"It is about people."},{"time":1019182,"text":"It's about how we can use technology"},{"time":1020816,"text":"to change the way we think"},{"time":1022862,"text":"and do and make music,"},{"time":1024306,"text":"and maybe even add to how we can"},{"time":1027992,"text":"connect with each other through music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1030502,"text":"And with that, I want to say,"},{"time":1032655,"text":"this is computer music, and thank you for listening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1035752,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}